
main features:
1. 3D navigation - you can drag left, right and zoom in and out. cells fade out as they move away from the Z focus range.
2. literate programming - you can intertwine code with text. you can create hyperlinks that send you to other cells.
3. meta-programs / customizable cells - cells can be programmed. this way you can configure the compiler for the language you want to use. you create classes of cells, which can be inherited to add domain-specific features.
4. beautiful and minimalistic
5. gallaxies and black holes - you can create a black hole to a new galaxy.
